title: Release branding for MsBuild.Engine.Corext package as well as
body:
The official build for 16.3.0 produced this set of packages:

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3347530/65181490-c9278900-da24-11e9-823f-5ed6267e47c5.png)

The mismatch on the Corext package caused confusion among (at least) one of its consumers that it wasn't the final package.

If possible, we should drop the version suffix there, too.

nodes.body: Team triage: this is cosmetic and we don't expect it to be worth much, so let's just close it.
